text:
Alright,
That should be all for the emergency exits.

Yeah, we should have
checked from end to end.

But Juri, you could've let me handle this stuff
and enjoyed yourself until the lessons.

Isn't that part of the camp too?
We shouldn't rely on the producer for everything.

It's not that we're not counting on you
it's just...

The producer has a lot to do, right?
We can handle safety checks and stuff too.

Yeah, I thought
you meant it that way from the start.
Come on, you should've said that earlier.

But really, I want to help you guys out.
I want you to enjoy the camp the most.

In that case, you don't have to worry.
It's bound to be fun, always.
